{"tid":786822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳浩天向特朗普發信　中華廠商會：鼓勵外國干預香港令人反感","createTime":"2018-08-20T08:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T09:29:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e1becde2ed4001acef160760ced0bddc65bbffbf","tid":786822,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180820/s00001/5e85d88fb49b6d1c8bd05b74a8e53656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180820%2Fs00001%2F5e85d88fb49b6d1c8bd05b74a8e53656.jpg&h=4530a17c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨召集人陳浩天日前向美國總統特朗普發公開信，稱鑑於香港自由迅速惡化，促請美國總統特朗普審視《美國&mdash;香港政策法》，撤銷香港和中國的世界貿易組織成員身分。香港中華廠商聯合會表示非常遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n廠商會表示，香港作為世貿創始成員，對自由貿易的信念一直堅定不移，且致力消除國際貿易壁壘。事實上，對香港這個細小且完全對外開放的經濟體系，一個強大而可靠的多邊貿易制度至為重要。根據數字，香港的貨物及服務貿易總額，相等於本地生產總值的375%，而貿易及物流更是本港的支柱產業，若香港被撤世貿成員的身份，後果將非常嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n廠商會指，美國對中國發動貿易戰且持續升級，香港一方面極不願意看到這種貿易保護主義抬頭；另一方面亦對貿易戰帶來的沖擊極為不安，不少港商已對前景表示憂慮，而陳浩天在這個非常時期，向美國提出此等無理及荒謬要求，無異出賣香港利益，對香港經濟構成重大威脅，亦鼓勵外國干預香港的內部事務，是非常不理智的行為，令人反感。<br />\n<br />\n廠商會重申反對陳浩天及香港民族黨的言行，並批評一切以個人的政治目的為藉口，危害香港整體利益行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180820/s00001/1534750410260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180820%2Fs00001%2F1534750410260&d=LDRqnxBZ3bCscDMT3EvQtIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b8baeb80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180820%2Fs00001%2F1534750410260&h=ddfe60b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180820/s00001/1534750410260</a>"},{"pid":"efb76ce4fc6e46c7cf0a3b888b4228b0b0e7d7ba","tid":786822,"uid":48139,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"廢左關係法咪無機會俾外國干涉內政囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016406e52544f13fab95c2379fac9a1b653eef1b","tid":786822,"uid":19978,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:12:07.000Z","msg":"宜家就係叫人唔好干預啊"},{"pid":"3ede99e86e4f3cffb6a4369f53c3c3a61fa9ccb9","tid":786822,"uid":50457,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"有關係法先係干預<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03481fde91fdf6362d224f53fb3df1787726f63","tid":786822,"uid":12021,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d370ec2da9a2795084414c4e47a949c115f9b96","tid":786822,"uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"我無反感wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2e11e3204e498db911644b70a6c790cf3b31ae","tid":786822,"uid":79563,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:14:14.000Z","msg":"《美國&mdash;香港政策法》係美國法律, 係美國國會既事<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天就係英國香港人<br />\n<br />\n你中華廠商會唔好干預美國既事"},{"pid":"93955230debb8c002106d9cabe04cb579348d508","tid":786822,"uid":29295,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:14:42.000Z","msg":"鼓勵中國干預香港令人反感"},{"pid":"9e6ac566480b47e390d9acf288672c61de6e5ec2","tid":786822,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"班友反應 大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a922fbbd0208f681a67b27c8334a24e4d0ca5769","tid":786822,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:16:46.000Z","msg":"廢咗關係法 軍事收回美國領事館"},{"pid":"9adbe812435b4e94fd597dffc09179bb598419fb","tid":786822,"uid":41500,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:22:13.000Z","msg":"你d死老野憑乜代